47:37.105 --> 47:39.023
[Anne Narrating]
Our blessed radio.

47:39.107 --> 47:43.277
It gives us our eyes and ears
out into the world.

47:43.362 --> 47:46.280
We listen to the German station
only for good music.

47:46.365 --> 47:49.283
