01:02:54.689 --> 01:02:57.691
â™ªâ™ª [Continues]

01:03:15.501 --> 01:03:18.962
It's so different
from what Mr. Kraler
tells us.

01:03:19.046 --> 01:03:21.673
Mr. Kraler says that
things are improving.

01:03:21.757 --> 01:03:25.677
I like it better
the way Kraler tells it.

