now open the gates â™ª

02:31:03.264 --> 02:31:06.057
â™ª Our allies have landed ashore â™ª

02:31:06.142 --> 02:31:09.185
â™ª We'll fight and we'll capture
our country again â™ª

02:31:09.270 --> 02:31:11.896
â™ª And freedom is ours evermore â™ª

02:31:11.981 --> 02:31:14.941
â™ª And freedom
is ours evermore â™ª

02:31:15.025 --> 02:31:19.738
â™ª In the name of Orange
now open the gates â™ª

02:31:19.822 --> 02:31:24.868
â™ª Our allies have landed on shore â™ª

02:31:24.952 --> 02:31:27.036
â™ª We'll fight â™ª

02:31:27.163 --> 02:31:31.750
â™ª And we'll capture
our country again â™ª
[Bell Tolling]

02:31:31.834 --> 02:31:33.752
Shh. Shh.

02:31:33.836 --> 02:31:38.423
[Whispering]
